</ul></nav></section><section class="front-matter"><div class="ameta p font-secondary font-xs">
<hgroup><h1>A Comparison between Human and NLP-based Annotation of Clinical Trial Eligibility Criteria Text Using The OMOP Common Data Model</h1></hgroup><div class="cg p">
<a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Li%20X"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id1"><span class="name western">Xinhang Li</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id1">
<h3><span class="name western">Xinhang Li</span></h3>
<div class="p">
