<sup>1,</sup><sup>#</sup>, <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Kury%20F"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id3"><span class="name western">Fabrício Kury</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id3">
<h3><span class="name western">Fabrício Kury</span></h3>
<div class="p">
